96350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"楂住個春袋，唔好放手呀（多圖)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474880</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場堅係春袋，唔好放棄！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">齋睇佢哋極速冚停就知<br />\n佢哋堅驚呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Fact</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 星期二：公佈全部航班Cancel，實情又唔係<br />\n2. 星期一：現場不停亂放風話機鐵停駛，又吹清場<br />\n3. 連續三日入機場，機管局網頁聲稱1及4停車場Full，路牌寫Full，門口都寫Full、入面係有位架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全撚部都係假嘅<br />\nOfficial公佈嘅消息都要做假<br />\n可想然知佢哋幾撚驚</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">只許持有效機票進入</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUhr6j2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUhr6j2.jpg&h=cff027bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om2S1Tq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom2S1Tq.jpg&h=17134eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Sbc1Tt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Sbc1Tt.jpg&h=a22f65ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">接機只可在門外食塵</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNtbx1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNtbx1c.jpg&h=7c74bed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一日成功係因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">夠人</span></span></strong>成條路塞曬<br />\n佢運作唔到<br />\n如果我哋第一日嘅全部人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">有車揸車<br />\n冇車搭巴士機鐵<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n癱瘓去機場嘅交通<br />\n佢一樣要停<br />\n絕對和理非又不損兵折將<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭成本低又舒服 <br />\n效果又大</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">夠人就塞交通<br />\n唔夠人都可以塞佢行人入口</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKoi4Ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKoi4Ji.jpg&h=3b72e203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係其中一個入口<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">，幾百人搞掂！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n需要大家支持<br />\n需要大量文宣配合<br />\n<br />\n你咪遊車河都出埋禁制令囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊諗掂佢呀！！！"}]}